ated with the\nreactions 12Be(p,t)10Be(gs) and 12Be(p,t)10Be(pv)(~10Be(p,t)8Be(gs)). In\nparticular, concerning this last reaction, predictions of \\sigma_{abs} can\nchange by an order of magnitude depending on whether the halo properties\nassociated with the d_{5/2} orbital are treated selfconsistently in calculating\nthe ground state correlations of the (pair removal) mode, or not.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2012 16:02:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-12"}
