ifferent frequencies. The observation of additional\nbinary pulsars with the SKA could reach a sensitivity of h_c ~ 3*10^(-17).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2012 20:50:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Mar 2013 07:38:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-27"}
