 local observables and a full\nprobabilistic interpretation, could lead to a coherent unification of an\nhypothetical discrete Planck scale with the usual Fermi scale of high-energy\nphysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Dec 2012 15:20:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Feb 2015 14:38:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-12"}
